00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:56,400
It increases, it intensifies,

252
00:10:57,120 --> 00:11:00,120
and the believers, they're scattered abroad,

253
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:02,120
but here's what happened.

254
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:05,160
As the enemy is fighting and the enemy is persecuting,

255
00:11:05,160 --> 00:11:07,160
the people of God are scattered.

256
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:09,720
The apostles stay there in Jerusalem

257
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:11,080
according to the text of scripture,

258
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:13,160
but we find that the people depart,

259
00:11:13,160 --> 00:11:14,000
and you know what they do?

